                        QuickStart for MathCollection


Preface
-------

This document describes how to use the package mathCollection by means of
two test programms.


Description for Unix/Linux
--------------------------

In the following the commands which can be executed are stated. Lines
beginning with a hashmark are comment lines.

# Create a directory.
mkdir MathCollection

# Change into the directory.
cd MathCollection

# Download the archive file mathCollection.tar.gz

# Extract the files of the archive.
tar -zxf mathCollection.tar.gz

# Download the archive file mathCollTests.tar.gz

# Extract the files of the archive.
tar -zxf mathCollTests.tar.gz

# Follow the description in file TEST.

